ors with high returns, then diverted funds into shell companies for unrelated ventures. This development marks a step towards justice for duped homebuyers and investors.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/promoters-of-srs-group-charged-in-2200-crore-money-laundering-scandal/125290515?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-57232/125290515.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}